(1, '7+TIPS+FOR+PLANNING+AN+OFF-ROAD+TRIP', 'Regular+road+trips+can+be+lots+of+fun%2C+but+driving+on+flat+stretches+of+highway+for+hours+on+end+can+get+redundant+after+a+while.+Off-road+trips+literally+and+figuratively+take+you+off+the+beaten+path%2C+creating+a+deeper+bond+between+yourself+and+your+vehicle.+Here+are+seven+tips+for+planning+an+adventurous+and+memorable+off-road+road+trip.%0D%0A%0D%0A1.+++++CHOOSE+A+MANAGEABLE+TERRAIN%0D%0AStart+by+researching+off-roading+destinations+and+finding+places+with+manageable+terrains.+These+are+the+different+types+of+off-roading%2C+in+order+from+the+least+to+most+challenging+environments%3A%0D%0A%0D%0AGreen+laning%3A+also+known+as+%E2%80%9Ctwo-tracking%2C%E2%80%9D+this+simple+form+of+off-roading+includes+driving+on+unpaved+roads+and+pathways+designed+for+off-road+vehicles.%0D%0ADune+bashing%3A+the+goal+of+this+off-roading+sub-genre+is+to+climb+up+and+down+sand+dunes+without+losing+control+of+the+vehicle.%0D%0ARock+crawling%3A+rock+crawling+is+the+stereotypical+type+of+off-roading+that+involves+navigating+rough+roads+with+large+immovable+obstacles%2C+namely+rocks+and+boulders.%0D%0AMudding%3A+this+type+off-roading+takes+you+through+wet+environments+with+lots+of+mud+and+clay.+It%E2%80%99s+arguably+the+most+challenging+type+because+vehicles+can+get+stuck+easily.%0D%0AChoose+destinations+that+you+know+you+can+handle.+Off-roading+is+already+dangerous+enough%2C+so+you+should+stay+within+your+experience+level+until+you+gain+more+confidence.+You+should+also+pick+destinations+with+scenic+views+and+other+tourist+attractions+nearby.%0D%0A%0D%0A2.+++++MAP+AND+MEMORIZE+THE+ROUTE%0D%0AOnce+you+find+the+perfect+destination%2C+map+out+and+memorize+the+route.+Look+up+videos%2C+images+and+reviews+from+other+off-roaders+and+try+to+visualize+yourself+on+the+trail.+Gaining+intimate+knowledge+of+the+terrain%E2%80%99s+various+obstacles+will+boost+your+confidence+and+navigation+skills.+The+same+logic+applies+to+hiking+trips+and+other+outdoor+adventures.%0D%0A%0D%0A3.+++++PROTECT+YOUR+VEHICLE%0D%0ANow+that+you%E2%80%99re+familiar+with+your+destination%E2%80%99s+layout%2C+you+can+take+the+appropriate+steps+to+protect+your+vehicle.+Adding+new+off-road+tires+and+wheels+will+provide+more+traction+and+raise+the+undercarriage+to+a+safer+height.+You+might+also+consider+adding+fender+flares%2C+brush+bars+and+other+safety+features+if+the+route+has+many+small+obstructions%2C+such+as+tree+branches.+When+it+comes+to+off-road+wheels%2C+GRID+Off-Road+has+a+vast+selection+of+off-road+wheel+options.+We+offer+both+forged+and+cast+off-road+rims+in+a+variety+of+styles+to+choose+from.+Whether+you%E2%80%99re+looking+for+truck+wheels+or+Jeep+wheels%2C+we+have+a+set+that+will+definitely+catch+your+eye%21%0D%0A%0D%0A4.+++++BE+A+FUEL-EFFICIENT+DRIVER%0D%0AYou+need+to+be+a+fuel-efficient+driver+at+all+times+during+your+road+trip.+Drive+at+60+miles+per+hour+on+highways+to+maximize+your+gas+mileage.+Try+not+to+idle+and+constantly+change+speeds.+Identify+the+most+optimal+gas+stops+before+the+trip+to+avoid+wasting+more+time+and+fuel+later.+Most+importantly%2C+you+should+bring+an+extra+can+of+gas+on+the+trail+if+you+run+out.+Your+vehicle%E2%80%99s+gas+mileage+takes+a+hit+from+the+additional+off-road+modifications%2C+so+a+full+tank+won%E2%80%99t+last+as+long+as+you+expect.%0D%0A%0D%0A5.+++++CHECK+THE+WEATHER+FORECAST%0D%0AKeep+a+close+watch+on+the+weather+forecast+in+the+days+preceding+your+trip.+Off-roading+in+inclement+weather+presents+many+new+challenges%2C+including+poor+traction%2C+low+visibility+and+unpredictable+trail+conditions.+The+type+of+weather+you+encounter+will+largely+determine+what+clothes+and+off-road+accessories+you%E2%80%99ll+need+to+bring.%0D%0A%0D%0A6.+++++PACK+FOR+THE+WORST%0D%0AWhen+planning+an+outdoor+adventure%2C+it%E2%80%99s+always+a+good+idea+to+prepare+for+the+worst.+Bring+any+clothes+you+might+need+%E2%80%93+hat%2C+gloves%2C+rain+jacket%2C+extra+layers%2C+etc.+%E2%80%93+even+if+the+forecast+calls+for+sunny+skies+and+mild+temperatures.+You+should+also+bring+these+off-road+items+to+get+yourself+out+of+tricky+situations%3A%0D%0A%0D%0ARecovery+boards%0D%0AElectric+winch%0D%0ATire+repair+kit%0D%0AAir+compressor%0D%0AMechanic+toolkit%0D%0ASolving+every+mishap+will+allow+you+to+drive+with+greater+peace+of+mind.+Instead+of+spending+the+whole+trip+worrying+about+a+flat+tire+or+bad+weather%2C+you+can+go+with+a+clear+head%2C+knowing+that+you+have+the+tools+to+address+the+problem.%0D%0A%0D%0A7.+++++BRING+A+FRIEND%0D%0AThe+buddy+system+is+the+most+important+rule+for+any+dangerous+activity.+It+would+be+best+if+you+had+a+companion+in+case+you+get+injured%2C+stranded+or+lost.+Plus%2C+driving+with+a+friend+is+always+more+fun.+You+get+to+experience+the+trials+and+tribulations+together+and+share+those+memories+for+the+rest+of+your+lives.%0D%0A%0D%0AENJOY+EVERY+MINUTE%0D%0ARoad+trips+seem+like+long+and+arduous+journeys+before+we+begin%2C+but+they+always+flash+by+in+the+blink+of+an+eye.+Make+sure+to+live+in+the+moment+and+enjoy+every+minute+of+your+off-road+road+trip.+Every+roadblock+is+a+learning+opportunity.+Embrace+the+highs+and+lows%2C+and+you+will+be+a+much+better+off-road+driver+at+your+journey%E2%80%99s+end.'),
(2, 'HOW+CAN+YOU+CUT+YOUR+OFF-ROAD+VEHICLE%E2%80%99S+FUEL+COSTS%3F', 'Off-roaders+always+expect+to+cause+some+sort+of+damage+to+their+vehicles+when+they+hit+the+trails.+But+these+days%2C+the+most+severe+damage+happens+at+the+gas+pump.%0D%0A%0D%0AFuel+prices+remain+incredibly+high+nationwide%2C+even+after+a+slight+drop.+Here+are+five+practical+ways+you+can+cut+your+off-road+vehicle%E2%80%99s+fuel+costs.%0D%0A%0D%0A1.+Develop+Fuel-Saving+Driving+Habits%0D%0A%0D%0AYour+vehicle%E2%80%99s+mileage+can+vary+widely+based+on+your+driving+habits.+You+can%E2%80%99t+afford+to+be+wasteful+with+gas+prices+at+their+current+levels.+Start+practicing+these+fuel-efficient+driving+habits+next+time+you+get+behind+the+wheel%3A%0D%0A%0D%0AStop+idling.%0D%0AFollow+the+speed+limit%2C+especially+on+highways.%0D%0AEase+up+on+the+gas+and+brake+pedals.%0D%0AAnticipate+the+flow+of+traffic+to+avoid+sudden+stops.%0D%0AOpen+the+windows+instead+of+blasting+the+A%2FC.%0D%0AUse+cruise+control+on+highways+if+your+vehicle+has+it.%0D%0AYou+should+also+map+out+the+most+fuel-efficient+route+each+time+you+drive.+As+all+off-roaders+know%2C+the+fastest+trail+isn%E2%80%99t+always+the+best.+A+path+with+many+stop+signs+and+red+lights+might+be+the+quickest%2C+but+you%E2%80%99re+burning+unnecessary+fuel+every+time+you+stop.+Taking+roads+with+fewer+stops+will+save+you+some+gas.%0D%0A%0D%0ASimilarly%2C+a+road+with+a+35-mph+speed+limit+may+burn+less+gas+than+a+road+with+a+50-mph+speed+limit.+Practicing+fuel-efficient+driving+habits+will+also+help+ensure+your+safety+while+off-roading+in+suboptimal+conditions.%0D%0A%0D%0A2.+Remove+Excess+Weight%0D%0A%0D%0AYour+off-road+vehicle+likely+has+tools%2C+outdoor+gear+and+other+miscellaneous+stuff+in+the+trunk.+This+additional+weight+forces+the+car+to+work+harder%2C+needlessly+increasing+its+gas+consumption.+Removing+100+pounds+can+save+about+1%25+of+fuel+per+gallon.+The+improvement+doesn%E2%80%99t+seem+like+much+in+the+short+term%2C+but+it+may+save+you+a+few+hundred+dollars+in+the+long+run.%0D%0A%0D%0AHowever%2C+you+shouldn%E2%80%99t+ditch+everything+and+go+barebones.+Hold+on+to+essential+items+like+the+spare+tire%2C+repair+kits+and+first+aid+supplies.+Safety+always+comes+first.%0D%0A%0D%0A3.+Take+Preventative+Maintenance+Seriously%0D%0A%0D%0AYour+car%E2%80%99s+ideal+fuel+efficiency+doesn%E2%80%99t+last+long+%E2%80%94+it+slowly+decreases+as+it+accumulates+more+damage.+That%E2%80%99s+why+staying+on+top+of+key+preventive+maintenance+tasks+is+critical.+Check+the+tire+pressure+regularly%2C+change+the+filters+as+needed+and+replace+the+engine+fluids+based+on+the+owner%E2%80%99s+manual%E2%80%99s+suggestions.%0D%0A%0D%0AIgnoring+minor+repairs+often+leads+to+severe+mechanical+failures.+A+total+breakdown+is+the+last+thing+you+want+while+off-roading.+If+you+can%E2%80%99t+identify+potential+problems+with+the+naked+eye%2C+consider+getting+a+telematics+device.+It+records+your+driving+behavior%2C+including+any+actions+that+may+lead+to+fuel+inefficiencies+or+mechanical+issues.%0D%0A%0D%0A4.+Choose+the+Right+Mods%0D%0A%0D%0AAll+modifications+should+improve+your+car%E2%80%99s+off-road+performance%2C+but+some+have+the+opposite+effect+on+fuel+efficiency.+Perhaps+the+most+notable+example+is+four-wheel+drive%2C+which+is+more+powerful+than+all-wheel+drive+on+rough+terrain+but+hurts+the+car%E2%80%99s+gas+mileage+as+a+result.%0D%0A%0D%0AYour+choice+of+tires+will+also+make+a+significant+impact.+A+set+of+bulky+off-roaders+with+good+traction+will+improve+performance%2C+safety+and+fuel+efficiency+in+one+fell+swoop.+There+are+several+easy+mods+you+can+use+that+might+help+your+vehicle+conserve+gas.+But+don%E2%80%99t+forget+about+some+GRID+Off-Road+wheels%21+You+still+need+your+rig+to+look+good+and+we%E2%80%99ve+got+plenty+of+forged+off-road+wheels+and+cast+off-road+wheels+to+choose+from%2C%0D%0A%0D%0A5.+Avoid+the+Roughest+Trails%0D%0A%0D%0AAnother+factor+to+consider+is+the+quality+of+the+driving+surface.+A+smooth+road+allows+the+car+to+build+steady+momentum+and+consume+the+minimum+amount+of+gas.+A+bumpy+one+disrupts+that+momentum%2C+forcing+the+engine+to+work+harder+and+burn+more+fuel.%0D%0A%0D%0AEveryone+knows+there%E2%80%99s+no+such+thing+as+a+smooth+off-road+trail.+Still%2C+you+should+try+to+avoid+the+roughest+trails+for+your+vehicle%E2%80%99s+sake+and+take+ones+that+won%E2%80%99t+put+too+much+strain+on+the+engine.%0D%0A%0D%0ASometimes+Money+is+Everything%0D%0A%0D%0APeople+often+say%2C+%E2%80%9CMoney+isn%E2%80%99t+everything%2C%E2%80%9D+but+that+phrase+doesn%E2%80%99t+apply+here.+Gas+prices+are+too+high+for+you+to+be+reckless+with+your+off-road+vehicle.+Take+your+car%E2%80%99s+fuel+costs+seriously+and+start+practicing+the+above+five+tips.'),
(3, '4WD+VS.+AWD%3A+WHICH+IS+BETTER+FOR+OFF', 'Four-wheel+drive+%284WD%29+and+all-wheel+drive+%28AWD%29+seem+like+similar+driving+systems+based+on+their+names%2C+but+they%E2%80%99re+quite+different+in+practice.+So%2C+which+option+makes+for+a+better+off-roading+experience%3F%0D%0A%0D%0ALet%E2%80%99s+put+them+head-to-head%2C+explore+the+pros+and+cons%2C+and+reach+a+final+verdict.%0D%0A%0D%0APROS+OF+4WD%0D%0AFour-wheel+drive+is+the+older+brother+of+the+two+systems%2C+going+back+to+locomotives+and+the+first+automobile+models+during+the+industrial+revolution.+Today%2C+you%E2%80%99ve+probably+seen+some+4WD+vehicles+driving+through+rugged+off-road+terrains+in+car+commercials.%0D%0A%0D%0A4WD+is+designed+to+send+torque+to+all+four+wheels%2C+increasing+the+vehicle%E2%80%99s+traction+and+power.+More+advanced+4WD+systems+can+operate+full-time%2C+but+most+4WD+cars+have+a+part-time+system+that+drivers+can+toggle+on+and+off.+When+the+system+activates%2C+it+locks+the+front+axle+to+the+drive+train+so+all+four+wheels+spin+in+unison.%0D%0A%0D%0A4WD+also+comes+with+higher+and+lower+gear+sets+called+4-high+and+4-low%2C+which+are+designed+for+specific+environments.+4-high+works+best+on+flat+terrains+such+as+roads+with+fresh+rain%2C+ice%2C+or+snowfall%2C+enabling+the+car+to+reach+55+mph+despite+less-than-ideal+conditions.+4-low+is+the+opposite%2C+working+best+on+shallow+streams+and+increasing+the+car%E2%80%99s+towing+capacity.%0D%0A%0D%0AAuto+manufacturers+also+often+pair+4WD+systems+with+heavy-duty+suspensions+and+other+unique+modifications%2C+enhancing+the+vehicle%E2%80%99s+off-road+performance+even+further.+Because+of+these+factors%2C+4WD+is+the+go-to+option+for+most+experienced+off-roaders.+However%2C+the+system+still+has+some+downsides.%0D%0A%0D%0ACONS+OF+4WD%0D%0AThe+ability+to+turn+4WD+on%2Foff+and+add+a+variety+of+modifications+might+seem+like+positive+things%2C+but+they+can+also+work+against+the+driver.+First+off%2C+the+driving+experience+is+noticeably+different.+The+pedals+are+stiff%2C+fuel+consumption+increases%2C+and+the+driver+has+to+pay+close+attention+to+their+speed.+For+example%2C+going+too+fast+in+4-low+can+cause+serious+damage+to+the+transfer+case.%0D%0A%0D%0AYou+also+can%E2%80%99t+shift+into+4WD+the+same+way+you+shift+gears+manually.+You+have+to+pull+over%2C+stop+the+car%2C+and+switch+to+neutral+first.+4WD+vehicles+are+also+heavier+and+more+expensive+on+average+than+other+cars%2C+which+could+nullify+the+system%E2%80%99s+positive+qualities+depending+on+which+off-roader+you+ask.+A+lighter+vehicle+is+almost+always+better+than+a+heavier+one.%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0APROS+OF+AWD%0D%0AAll-wheel+drive+has+a+similar+function+to+4WD%3A+improving+the+car%E2%80%99s+traction+and+power+on+flat+terrains+with+ice%2C+snow%2C+and+other+debris.+However%2C+the+system+toggles+on+and+off+automatically%2C+allowing+the+driver+to+stay+on+course+without+missing+a+beat.%0D%0A%0D%0AThe+ability+to+automatically+redistribute+power+to+individual+wheels+ensures+the+best+traction+possible+when+the+system+is+turned+on.+Plus%2C+AWD+doesn%E2%80%99t+guzzle+fuel+like+4WD%2C+giving+it+a+clear+advantage+in+consistency+and+fuel+economy.%0D%0A%0D%0ACONS+OF+AWD%0D%0AAlthough+AWD+is+easier+on+the+driver+and+the+gas+tank%2C+it+doesn%E2%80%99t+come+close+to+4WD%E2%80%99s+off-road+capabilities.+It+improves+traction+on+man-made+roads%2C+but+it%E2%80%99s+not+as+effective+in+the+wilderness+where+the+%E2%80%9Croads%E2%80%9D+are+less+flat+and+more+unpredictable.+There+aren%E2%80%99t+any+extra+high+or+low+gears+to+help+you+climb+a+steep+boulder+or+power+through+a+mud+puddle.%0D%0A%0D%0APlus%2C+the+AWD+system+doesn%E2%80%99t+always+turn+on+when+the+driver+wants+it.+When+given+the+choice+between+fuel+efficiency+and+more+traction%2C+the+system+will+choose+fuel+efficiency+100%25+of+the+time.+It+only+turns+on+if+it+senses+the+vehicle+losing+traction%2C+but+by+then+it+could+already+be+too+late.%0D%0A%0D%0AIf+you%E2%80%99re+going+to+take+an+AWD+vehicle+off-roading%2C+you+have+to+do+some+serious+prep+work+to+ensure+the+car+makes+it+through+the+trip.%0D%0A%0D%0ATHE+VERDICT%3A+4WD+REIGNS+SUPREME%0D%0ABased+on+our+comparison%2C+4WD+is+the+clear+winner+for+off-roading+purposes.+4WD+vehicles+might+be+heavier+and+more+expensive%2C+but+they+have+the+capabilities+to+justify+it.+AWD+is+better+suited+for+everyday+drivers%2C+helping+them+navigate+man-made+roads+with+poor+traction.+Other+off-road+adventures+are+best+left+to+beefy+4WD+vehicles.%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0AFord+truck+on+GD12+GRID+Off-Road+wheels%0D%0A%0D%0ASo+if+you%E2%80%99re+looking+to+add+some+extra+style+to+your+4-wheeler%2C+definitely+add+some+GRID+Off-Road+wheels+to+it%21+Our+off-road+wheels+are+made+to+fit+a+variety+of+4%C3%974+vehicles%2C+from+Jeeps+to+Broncos%2C+trucks%2C+and+SUVs.+We+have+two+types+of+off-road+wheels%3A+forged+off-road+wheels+and+cast+off-road+wheels.+Our+GF+collection+is+all+forged+and+there+are+countless+wheel+styles+to+choose+from%21+The+same+is+true+for+our+GD+cast+off-road+wheel+collection%2C+which+is+very+popular+with+many+4WD+enthusiasts.+If+you+like+an+off-road+wheel+from+our+collection%2C+email+us+at+sales%40grid-offroad.com+so+we+can+help+locate+an+authorized+GRID+dealer+near+you%21+%0D%0A%0D%0A'),
(4, 'HOW+TO+PROTECT+YOUR+OFF-ROAD+VEHICLE%E2%80%99S+EXTERIOR', 'When+you%E2%80%99re+in+your+off-road+vehicle%2C+the+last+thing+you+should+be+thinking+about+is+if+it%E2%80%99s+going+to+make+it+through+the+next+trip.+Preparing+ahead+of+time+lets+you+focus+on+the+ride.+Let+loose+by+protecting+your+off-roader%E2%80%99s+exterior%21+Need+a+place+to+start%3F+Here+are+six+tips+on+how+to+keep+your+vehicle%E2%80%99s+body+strong.%0D%0A%0D%0ATHE+IMPORTANCE+OF+SAFETY%0D%0ABecause+of+the+often-rough+terrain%2C+off-road+vehicles+can+experience+a+lot+of+damage.+Some+of+the+most+common+you+can+experience+are%3A%0D%0A%0D%0ATransmission+issues%0D%0ATire+damage%0D%0AUndercarriage+damage%0D%0AMisalignment%0D%0AAll+of+these+problems+will+cause+more+issues+down+the+road.+Not+addressing+them+soon+enough+can+lead+to+more+expensive+repairs+and+a+lower+resale+value.+The+best+solution%3F+Protect+your+off-roader+with+exterior+modifications+before+these+things+can+happen%21%0D%0A%0D%0ATIPS+FOR+PROTECTING+YOUR+OFF-ROAD+VEHICLE%E2%80%99S+EXTERIOR%0D%0ARig+your+vehicle+up+protectively+to+keep+it+out+there+as+long+as+possible.+Stay+out+longer+with+a+tough+surface+that+saves+your+off-roader+from+harmful+damage+and+scratches.%0D%0A%0D%0A1.+++++GET+THE+RIGHT+TIRES%0D%0AThe+size+of+a+tire+is+extremely+important+to+an+off-road+vehicle.+They%E2%80%99re+required+to+reach+the+perfect+suspension%2C+fit+the+brake+calipers+and+even+give+you+a+different+style.+With+so+many+tires+out+there%2C+you+need+to+find+the+best+ones+for+your+vehicle.+Good+tires+will+save+your+undercarriage+and+give+you+an+awesome+new+look%21%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A2.+++++GIVE+IT+A+GOOD+COATING%0D%0ALike+tires%2C+you+may+think+of+coatings+as+ways+to+just+protect+the+paint+job.+While+that+is+part+of+their+purpose%2C+waxes+and+ceramics+can+also+save+your+exterior+from+damaging+weather+like+rain+and+UV+rays.+Coating+your+off-roader+will+help+protect+it+from+debris+and+potential+rust.+Think+of+it+as+an+extra+layer+of+defense.%0D%0A%0D%0AUse+wax+if+you%E2%80%99re+interested+in+reapplying+the+coating+during+washes+or+maintenance.+Ceramic+coatings+last+a+lot+longer%2C+so+use+these+when+you+want+to+reapply+less+and+prevent+scratches.%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A3.+++++FIND+4%C3%974+BODY+ARMOR%0D%0AA+newer+feature+for+off-road+vehicles%2C+companies+are+introducing+4%C3%974+customizable+body+armor.+You+can+install+it+before+heading+out+and+enjoy+your+ride+without+thinking+about+potential+dents+and+scratches.+While+damage+to+the+paint+seems+like+having+a+cool+scar%2C+body+armor+is+more+than+that.+It+saves+you+from+costly+repairs+and+is+another+opportunity+for+intense+styles%21%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A4.+++++CLEAN+YOUR+VEHICLE+WELL%0D%0AAs+you+know%2C+your+off-roader+is+going+to+get+dirty+while+you%E2%80%99re+riding.+To+keep+it+in+shape%2C+a+good+cleaning+routine+is+vital.+Any+debris+that+gets+stuck+in+your+vehicle+can+cause+stains%2C+scratches+and+rust.+When+you%E2%80%99re+doing+detailing+at+home%2C+make+sure+you%E2%80%99re+following+the+right+steps+to+keep+your+off-roader+looking+good+and+staying+strong.%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A5.+++++PROTECT+THE+UNDERCARRIAGE%0D%0AThe+undercarriage+is+the+most+sensitive+part+of+your+off-road+vehicle.+Besides+the+frame%2C+it%E2%80%99s+exposed+to+the+most+potential+damage+while+you%E2%80%99re+driving.+Even+regular+streetcars+can+experience+damage+from+road+salt+and+moisture.%0D%0A%0D%0AFind+products+to+keep+your+undercarriage+safe.+Fluid+coatings+can+keep+out+the+salt+and+water+but+you%E2%80%99ll+need+to+reapply+them+for+full+strength.+Things+like+skid+plates+and+rock+sliders+are+physical+upgrades+that+keep+harmful+materials+out+of+your+undercarriage.+Research+your+options+to+find+out+which+one+is+right+for+you.%0D%0A%0D%0A6.+++++USE+FLARES+AND+BRUSH+BARS%0D%0AFender+flares+give+your+tires+extra+protection+and+may+be+legally+required+in+your+area%2C+depending+on+the+size.+However%2C+while+you%E2%80%99re+off-roading%2C+they+can+do+a+lot+to+reduce+the+damage+you+take.+On+top+of+protecting+your+tires%2C+they+also+keep+other+vehicles+from+any+debris+your+off-roader+might+lose+as+you%E2%80%99re+driving.%0D%0A%0D%0AAlso+known+as+brush+grilles+or+guards%2C+brush+bars+push+debris+out+of+your+way.+It+protects+your+exterior+by+getting+rid+of+any+plant+material+from+your+path+and+absorbing+the+shock+in+a+potential+collision.+On+top+of+making+your+vehicle+stronger%2C+it+also+helps+it+look+tougher.+Use+flares+and+brush+guards+to+give+your+off-roader+some+extra+physical+and+visual+power%21%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0APROTECT+YOUR+VEHICLE%E2%80%99S+EXTERIOR%0D%0AThe+best+way+to+defend+your+off-roader%E2%80%99s+interior+is+to+protect+its+exterior.+While+driving%2C+it+is+its+armor+against+whatever+might+damage+it.+Give+your+off-road+vehicle+the+protection+it+deserves%2C+starting+with+its+exterior.'),
(5, 'PROTECTING+YOUR+RIG+FROM+THEFT%3A+6+NEED-TO-KNOW+TIPS', 'Rugged+and+off-road+rigs+draw+a+lot+of+attention%2C+and+rightfully+so.+They+look+cool%2C+are+beasts+and+turn+heads+wherever+they+go.+They+also+tend+to+have+expensive+mods+and+parts+and+can+be+easier+to+access+without+a+key%2C+making+them+attractive+targets+for+thieves.%0D%0A%0D%0AYou+need+to+take+extra+precautions+to+keep+your+truck%2C+Jeep+or+SUV+rig+safe.+Here+are+five+need-to-know+tips+about+protecting+your+rig+from+theft.%0D%0A%0D%0A1.+++++Write+a+Common-Sense+Checklist%0D%0A%0D%0AMore+than+700%2C000+car%2C+truck+and+vehicle+thefts+occur+every+year%2C+and+the+main+reason+is+that+people+simply+fail+to+lock+them+or+leave+their+keys+inside.+You+can+avoid+these+mistakes+by+writing+a+common-sense+checklist+and+keeping+it+in+your+rig.+Your+list+might+look+something+like+this%3A%0D%0A%0D%0AClose+the+windows%0D%0AActivate+the+emergency+brake%0D%0ATurn+off+the+car%E2%80%99s+Bluetooth+and+W-Fi+features%2C+if+applicable%0D%0ATurn+off+the+vehicle%0D%0AGrab+your+phone%2C+wallet+and+other+essential+belongings%0D%0AExit+the+car+and+lock+the+vehicle%0D%0ATest+the+door+handles+to+make+sure+every+entrance+is+locked.%0D%0AYou+might+assume+you+can+remember+these+simple+steps%2C+but+a+thief+only+needs+you+to+make+a+mistake+one+time.+Eliminate+that+possibility+with+a+common-sense+checklist.%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A2.+++++ADD+THEFT+PROTECTION+DEVICES%0D%0AYou+can+also+install+various+theft+protection+devices+to+help+keep+your+rig+safe.+Some+are+inexpensive+tools+that+prevent+the+rig+from+moving%3A%0D%0A%0D%0ASteering+wheel+lock%3A+Prevents+the+steering+wheel+from+moving+more+than+a+few+inches%0D%0ABrake+and+clutch+lock%3A+Keeps+the+desired+pedal+locked+in+place%0D%0AWheel+clamp%3A+Attaches+to+your+GRID+wheels+to+prevent+the+tire+from+spinning%0D%0AThese+devices+will+stop+most+thieves+in+their+tracks%2C+but+well-equipped+carjackers+have+the+tools+to+remove+them.+Plus%2C+clamps+might+not+fit+on+an+old+rig%E2%80%99s+wheels.+If+you+want+to+use+this+tool%2C+consider+investing+in+strong+and+light+forged+GF+wheels+from+GRID%2C+which+can+handle+anything+you+throw+at+them.+You+can+also+take+your+vehicle%E2%80%99s+security+even+further+with+these+electronic+devices%3A%0D%0A%0D%0AAftermarket+alarm+system%3A+You+can+install+an+aftermarket+system+if+your+older+rig+does+not+have+a+built-in+alarm.%0D%0AImmobilizers%3A+Fuse+cutoffs%2C+kill+switches+and+ignition+disablers+prevent+the+vehicle+from+starting+until+a+hidden+button+is+activated.%0D%0AGPS+tracker%3A+This+hidden+device+allows+you+to+track+your+rig%E2%80%99s+location+if+it+gets+stolen.%0D%0ASome+rigs+also+come+with+additional+security+features+like+four-digit+access+codes.+Consider+yourself+lucky+you+have+another+line+of+defense+if+your+rig+has+one+of+these+features.%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0AMIND+WHERE+YOU+PARK%0D%0ARig+owners+are+often+selective+with+their+public+parking+spaces+to+avoid+getting+dents+and+scratches%2C+but+this+habit+can+also+ward+off+thieves.+Here+are+some+places+you+should+avoid%3A%0D%0A%0D%0AParking+lots+with+poor+lighting%0D%0AHigh-crime+areas%0D%0AThin+alleyways%0D%0AStreets+with+little+traffic%0D%0AMost+responsible+rig+owners+can+tell+if+a+parking+space+is+sketchy+right+away.+Listen+to+that+intuition+and+find+another+spot.+Try+to+park+in+areas+with+solid+lighting+and+constant+activity.+If+a+parking+garage+is+available+for+a+reasonable+price%2C+take+advantage+of+its+guards+and+cameras.%0D%0A%0D%0AYou+might+also+invest+in+a+rig+cover+to+hide+your+vehicle+in+plain+sight.+With+the+exterior+hidden+from+view%2C+it+looks+like+any+other+truck%2C+Jeep+or+SUV.+It+also+acts+as+another+frustrating+obstacle+for+thieves+to+get+through.%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A4.+++++KEEP+YOUR+RIG+CLEAN%0D%0AYou+should+maintain+your+rig%E2%80%99s+cleanliness+%E2%80%94+both+inside+and+out+%E2%80%94+to+discourage+thieves+from+trying+their+luck.+Wash+the+exterior+and+keep+the+interior+organized.+A+tidy+vehicle+tells+thieves+you+might+have+it+under+surveillance.+It+also+suggests+that+it+might+have+hidden+security+features+inside.%0D%0A%0D%0AA+spotless+exterior+also+makes+it+easier+to+spot+a+crucial+piece+of+evidence%3A+fingerprints.+If+someone+tries+to+break+into+your+freshly+cleaned+vehicle%2C+you+might+find+their+prints+and+report+your+findings+to+the+police.%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A5.+++++HIDE+YOUR+VALUABLES%0D%0ASometimes+car+thefts+occur+because+thieves+walk+by+a+vehicle+and+see+valuables+inside.+They+had+no+prior+intention+of+stealing+the+rig%2C+but+the+inner+contents+caught+their+attention.+You+can+make+your+rig+less+of+a+target+by+hiding+your+valuables+in+unlikely+places+like+inside+the+fuse+box+or+under+the+backseat.%0D%0A%0D%0ABetter+yet%2C+remove+all+valuables+from+your+car+and+leave+nothing+to+chance.+Keep+only+the+essentials+%E2%80%94+owner%E2%80%99s+manual%2C+car+registration%2C+roadside+assistance+info+%E2%80%94+and+take+everything+else+out+of+the+picture.+If+a+thief+manages+to+get+inside%2C+they%E2%80%99ll+realize+you+have+nothing+they+want+and+might+give+up+before+causing+further+damage.%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A6.+STEP+UP+YOUR+SECURITY+EFFORTS%0D%0ANone+of+us+can+entirely+rely+on+a+built-in+security+system%2C+let+alone+rigowners.+You+need+to+step+up+your+security+efforts+to+keep+your+prized+possession+safe.+Humble+yourself+and+write+that+common-sense+checklist.+Invest+in+more+security+measures%2C+including+simple+tasks+like+parking+and+cleaning.+These+tips+will+protect+your+rig+from+theft+and+ensure+it+stays+in+your+hands+for+the+foreseeable+future.');

